# NIFYA Authentication Service

This document describes the structure of the NIFYA authentication service.

## Key Files

- [package.json](mdc:Authentication-Service/package.json) - Package dependencies and scripts
- [Dockerfile](mdc:Authentication-Service/Dockerfile) - Docker configuration for containerization
- [README.md](mdc:Authentication-Service/README.md) - Service documentation
- [FIREBASE_INTEGRATION_PLAN.md](mdc:Authentication-Service/FIREBASE_INTEGRATION_PLAN.md) - Firebase integration documentation

## Source Code

The authentication service source code is organized in the [src](mdc:Authentication-Service/src/) directory.

